column1: #text=The library called and a book that I had asked to be notified when it came back to the library was back in .
#text=I drove to the library that is downtown .
#text=I went up to the librarians ' desk and asked for my book .
#text=The librarian went away to a set of shelves behind the counter and returned with the book .
#text=I went and sat on a chair and looked the book over to see if it was something that I really did want to read .
#text=The book looked interesting so I went back to the counter and waited in line .
#text=I found my library card in my wallet and waited some more .
#text=The librarian came over and smiled at me .
#text=Then when it was my turn at the counter , I handed the book to the person behind the desk .
#text=She scanned my library card and the book .
#text=I left the library with book in hand .
